{"summary":"Sharma had been with Meta for six years in various positions. ","webName":"theblock.co","link":"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/166102\/metas-horizon-metaverse-software-vp-sharma-leaving-company-cnbc","publishDate":"2022-08-27T07:12:30","id":1198,"type":null,"title":"Horizon software VP Sharma is leaving Meta: CNBC ","category":["COMPANIES"],"content":["<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Vivek Sharma, vice president of Meta\u2019s Horizon social media virtual reality (VR) software, is leaving the company, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cnbc.com\/2022\/08\/26\/meta-horizon-vp-vivek-sharma-leaving.html\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">CNBC reported<\/span><\/a><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> on Friday, citing a company spokesperson.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:0,&quot;335551620&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Sharma had been&nbsp;with Meta for six years in various positions.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:0,&quot;335551620&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The report said that Sharma oversaw VR projects including the Horizon Worlds social media service, Horizon Workrooms and the Horizon Venues app.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:0,&quot;335551620&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The Horizon team will now report directly to Vishal Shah, Meta\u2019s VP of the metaverse, CNBC said.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:0,&quot;335551620&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Last month, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/159920\/metas-metaverse-division-reality-labs-lost-2-8-billion-in-q2-2022\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Meta reported earnings<\/span><\/a><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> of $28.8 billion and earnings per share of $2.46 for the second quarter, both below estimates.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<em data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">This story's headline has been updated.<\/em>","© 2023 The Block. All Rights Reserved. This article is provided for informational purposes only. It is not offered or intended to be used as legal, tax, investment, financial, or other advice."],"entity":[{"type":"Meta\u2019s Horizon","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Sharma","content":"PERSON"},{"type":"Vivek Sharma","content":"PERSON"},{"type":"$2.46","content":"MONEY"},{"type":"2023","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Friday","content":"DATE"},{"type":"$28.8 billion","content":"MONEY"},{"type":"CNBC","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"second quarter","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Vishal Shah","content":"PERSON"}],"hashtag":[],"authors":["Mike Millard","The Block"]}